section.section:
In addition to the application, an applicant for initial licensure shall submit to the Secretary:
Information concerning any license or certification held by the applicant under the Health Occupations Article or under this article, including the prior or current operation by the applicant of a health care facility, residential facility, or similar health care program;
Information demonstrating the financial and administrative ability of the applicant to operate an assisted living program in compliance with this subtitle;
The policies and procedures to be implemented by the assisted living program;
Identification of the personnel and relief personnel to be employed by the assisted living program; and
Any other information that is relevant to the ability of the applicant to care for the residents of the assisted living program.
